<p>The <tt>add</tt> instruction is used to perform an addition.
</p>
<h1><span class="mw-headline" id="Syntax">Syntax</span></h1>
<pre>add <i>destination</i>, <i>value</i>
</pre>
<h1><span class="mw-headline" id="Examples">Examples</span></h1>
<dl><dt><tt>add eax, 0x10</tt></dt>
<dd>Add <tt>0x10</tt> to <tt>EAX</tt>.</dd>
<dt><tt>add eax, ebx</tt></dt>
<dd>Add <tt>EBX</tt> to <tt>EAX</tt> and store the result in <tt>EAX</tt>.</dd></dl>